_sText:
REMEMBER THE  FUTURE!

DE_HALFLANDIA customized by Zerg.
based from the original Valve DE_PIRANESI map.

It is the final version of a map  de_halflandia_beta http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/64327

On a map are present striders and ant lions. From ceilings long tongues of Barnacles hang down. Zombie attacks the player ...

A little mistakes and bugs are corrected. Productivity, especially on bombplace B is raised.

Illumination on a map is made more natural.  Skybox is made more detailed.

To contact a smooth map, as in cs1.6. All details are made by illusion or smoothed by clips.

Overview and nav-Files are attached inside the map. (nav by Chizbone)


THX TO THE ORIGINAL AUTHORs OF DE_PIRANESI.
